WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:06.507
Hello, my name is Brandon, and I'm going to tell you about a visitation I had from the Lord.

00:00:06.508 --> 00:00:17.230
I don't know if it was a dream or an out-of-body experience; all I know is that it changed my life forever.

00:00:17.231 --> 00:00:22.713
I'm just going to get right into it and tell you what happened.

00:00:22.715 --> 00:00:51.375
It was a normal night on July 6, 2014. I went to bed, and what happened next is mind-blowing. I want you to give me a little bit of your time.

00:00:51.376 --> 00:01:00.622
What I am about to tell you will change your life forever if you let it and meditate on what is about to happen.

00:01:00.623 --> 00:01:15.436
Earth as we know it, everything we see on a day-to-day basis, is about to change—from the biggest thing to the smallest thing.

00:01:15.437 --> 00:01:23.919
This is what happened: I went to bed, and suddenly I was taken out of my body.

00:01:23.920 --> 00:01:33.109
In a dream, you don't smell, taste, or feel heat the way I did.

00:01:33.110 --> 00:01:41.742
Suddenly, I was standing at a courthouse, and I looked over to my right; Jesus was standing right there next to me.

00:01:41.743 --> 00:01:58.472
He was looking at me. I looked around, and there were people rioting and burning cars.

00:01:58.473 --> 00:02:02.997
People were destroying things, throwing things, acting crazy.

00:02:02.998 --> 00:02:10.988
I was taken aback by what I saw because I could smell the smoke and the fires.

00:02:10.989 --> 00:02:18.313
I could see the courthouse on fire and mass chaos everywhere.

00:02:18.314 --> 00:02:25.679
A lady ran up to me, and I asked, "What is going on?"She said, "Don't you know?

00:02:25.680 --> 00:02:34.825
Didn't you see? All the Christians are gone. All the Christians are gone."I asked, "Where did they go?

00:02:34.826 --> 00:02:48.707
What happened?"She said the aliens came and took them. Suddenly, I looked up, and there were lightning strikes all over the sky.

00:02:48.708 --> 00:03:05.518
It looked like a major storm, but there was no rain. I could see lightning in the clouds; they were active, like an electric storm.

00:03:05.519 --> 00:03:29.903
As I looked across the town, I saw fires burning in many buildings—nearly all of them. Everyone was looting and stealing, acting godless.

00:03:29.904 --> 00:04:03.279
I want to interject something: every person, even the greatest sinner, wakes up with a sense of peace they don't realize they have. I call this the prayer covering of the church.

00:04:03.280 --> 00:04:26.242
There is a covering from the praying people of the church that covers the whole world, bringing an atmosphere of peace and comfort that people don't realize is there.

00:04:26.243 --> 00:04:36.902
When the rapture of the church takes place, that prayer covering is removed for the first time.

00:04:36.903 --> 00:04:47.279
There is total anarchy because people feel the void where that peace was, and they are freaking out.

00:04:47.280 --> 00:04:59.884
I felt that so strongly in the atmosphere; it was eerie and scary.

00:04:59.885 --> 00:05:17.322
Suddenly, I was taken to another scene. Jesus and I were suddenly in Berlin.

00:05:17.323 --> 00:05:46.522
I saw a man dressed in an expensive gray suit, a white shirt, and a nice tie getting out of a presidential-style limousine.

00:05:46.523 --> 00:06:20.552
He was driven to a massive conference room in Berlin where people from all the nations of the world were gathering at a large round table.

00:06:20.553 --> 00:06:47.412
He sat at the head. I could not see his face because the Lord had blotted it out, but I could see his confident stature as the leaders listened to his plan.

00:06:47.413 --> 00:06:47.938
This occurred shortly after the rapture, perhaps within a few hours.

00:06:47.939 --> 00:07:23.829
Everyone listened to him because he possessed a sense of confidence and peace similar to what the church used to provide.

00:07:23.830 --> 00:07:42.660
His presence brought a sense of calm that made everyone want to listen.

00:07:42.661 --> 00:08:15.459
Their eyes were fixed on him as he proposed a plan for a one-world currency and a chip.

00:08:15.460 --> 00:08:31.083
Every world leader surrendered their power to him during that single meeting. Then I was taken back to the courthouse.

00:08:31.084 --> 00:09:11.779
There was a mandate, shown on TVs everywhere, for people to bring all Bibles to public places like police stations or town squares because owning one was no longer allowed.

00:09:11.780 --> 00:09:27.710
They told people they could check out their Bibles later, but anyone who did was marked as a rebel.

00:09:27.711 --> 00:09:51.349
Eventually, they took the Bibles and burned them. I saw massive mounds of Bibles burning everywhere, creating huge smokestacks.

00:09:51.350 --> 00:10:10.713
This was happening in towns all around the world. It was against the law to have a Bible.

00:10:10.714 --> 00:10:23.963
Then I saw him take down city, state, and American flags and replace them with his own.

00:10:23.964 --> 00:10:41.716
And he put them on every courthouse over all the major public buildings that we would see an American flag, or wherever you are, your country flag, the French flag, the German flag, or the United Kingdom flag.

00:10:41.717 --> 00:10:51.680
They took those flags down and they put his flag up. And I'm going to show you right now what that flag looks like.

00:10:51.681 --> 00:10:59.987
I remember every bit of this clearly back from 2014 whenever the Lord showed me all this, what that flag looks like.

00:10:59.988 --> 00:11:26.677
And it's two swords with palm branches on the top of it, and they're golden, and there's like a globe in the middle, and there was black, white, and green, and it represented ISIS, al-Qaeda, and Hamas.

00:11:26.678 --> 00:11:36.263
All these terrorist organizations were bringing forth what they called—now I will tell you the name of what everybody called him—the Mahdi.

00:11:36.264 --> 00:11:43.989
I hope I don't butcher that, but that's what they called him. And everybody called this man the Mahdi.

00:11:43.990 --> 00:12:08.039
And every time you see him—look, I don't want to skip around here too much—but they put the flag up like I'm saying, and it was honor to him, the Mahdi, bringing him into power.

00:12:08.040 --> 00:12:25.991
Now I see public squares with big huge movie screens, massive movie screens that are as big as a huge building.

00:12:25.992 --> 00:12:36.682
But on Fridays, everybody dresses in white garments. They dress in like white robes by law.

00:12:36.683 --> 00:12:51.599
You go and on Fridays they have lines. All the people are in lines and they worship him on Fridays with the screen.

00:12:51.600 --> 00:13:03.174
Some of it's live playback and some of it is pre-recorded because you can't worship all around the world in the daytime because it's not daytime everywhere.

00:13:03.175 --> 00:13:20.977
But they were taken, and even where—I know I told you all in a previous video, if you go look at some of my stuff before—where they worship, and it's at a big Mason temple.

00:13:20.978 --> 00:13:34.848
It's at a huge Freemason's temple. They have huge white screens all on the front of this building and this is where the people come on Fridays to worship the antichrist.

00:13:34.849 --> 00:13:38.518
They're in single file lines and they all gather in these fields.

00:13:38.519 --> 00:13:44.159
Now, fill in the field—it goes way back there and it goes all the way around the building, the whole building.

00:13:44.160 --> 00:13:51.313
And this is where all the townspeople from all the major towns come and they start worshiping the antichrist.

00:13:51.314 --> 00:14:12.913
I saw him worshiping in Rome at the place where the Catholics worship, by where the pope is, that square, the Catholic church and the Vatican.

00:14:12.914 --> 00:14:18.495
They have major screens there. They have major screens in Europe and in Paris.

00:14:18.496 --> 00:14:28.683
It's everywhere. Even at Buckingham Palace, they had them there.

00:14:28.684 --> 00:14:35.474
I'm telling you, they're everywhere. And the people are required to worship on Fridays.

00:14:35.475 --> 00:14:53.822
So, that's a lot of detail with that. Now, I'm going to go another direction here to tell you all what happens. I was shown the mark of the beast. I was shown what it is.

00:14:53.823 --> 00:15:04.638
And I believe—and I'm not saying it's Neuralink—but I'm saying it is a type of Neuralink what Elon Musk is working on.

00:15:04.639 --> 00:15:12.624
I'm not saying it is that, but it's that kind of technology. It's very small.

00:15:12.625 --> 00:15:22.807
But what happens is they inject it in your hand or they inject it in your forehead.

00:15:22.808 --> 00:15:42.888
And I saw all the children—and I want to say this clearly—all children were taken out of here at the rapture of the church, all the way up until what I believe was the age of 15 or 16 years old.

00:15:42.889 --> 00:15:54.052
I'm not exactly sure of the age because I did not hear anybody talking about what the age bracket of those kids was.

00:15:54.053 --> 00:16:03.398
But all the children up until the age of accountability were gone.

00:16:03.399 --> 00:16:13.838
Now, people are still going to have babies during the tribulation. Life is still going on.

00:16:13.839 --> 00:16:27.999
There are seven years of tribulation: three and a half years of not great tribulation and then three and a half years of great tribulation.

00:16:28.000 --> 00:16:35.265
But people are still creating and making babies and having families during the tribulation.

00:16:35.266 --> 00:16:42.985
So if they have a child during the tribulation, they are still here.

00:16:42.986 --> 00:16:47.198
Those children are here. That's what I'm trying to tell you.

00:16:47.199 --> 00:16:55.693
Remember the Bible says, "Woe to those that give suck in those days, that are breastfeeding and have children in those days."Woe to those.

00:16:55.694 --> 00:17:01.580
It even talks about it in the word. But people are still having children.

00:17:01.581 --> 00:17:11.692
So I want you to understand that because I don't want any confusion to go, "Well, why were there kids here?"or whatever for what I'm about to tell you.

00:17:11.693 --> 00:17:25.078
Now I'm going to go, and the Lord showed me this. I saw a lot of Christians that were furious that they were left.

00:17:25.079 --> 00:17:33.569
Now, I heard the Lord say this: they were upset because they preached a lukewarm gospel.

00:17:33.570 --> 00:17:59.390
They preached a sappy, watered-down grace message that they could live the way they wanted to live—a lot of people living in sin and still making it to heaven, that everything was okay with them, that they could just live like the world and still make it in the rapture of the church.

00:17:59.391 --> 00:18:13.506
And what happened? There were pastors that were preaching a compromising, lukewarm gospel that were left, and they were still here during the tribulation.

00:18:13.507 --> 00:18:26.983
And those congregation members were so mad because of the way they got preached the gospel that they were ready to kill those preachers. They were fuming mad.

00:18:26.984 --> 00:18:47.569
And I saw people that I knew that were left here during the tribulation that thought they would—I know them personally because I worked at a large church—and some of these people were major givers.

00:18:47.570 --> 00:19:09.093
And when they were left, I saw one lady in particular flipping the Lord off and giving him the finger because she was left during the tribulation and was cussing and acting crazy because she was angry she was still here, because she thought she should go.

00:19:09.094 --> 00:19:24.772
But her heart was obviously full of poison and she was vile. And I'm telling you, I saw this woman go immediately whenever the mark of the beast was given out; she was one of the first to take the mark.

00:19:24.773 --> 00:19:43.592
I remember seeing this, but there were pastors and preachers that I saw personally, and as of right now see them on TV on a weekly basis, that were left, and those congregation members were ready to string them up.

00:19:43.593 --> 00:19:56.338
It was that serious. People were upset. These pastors were on TBN and some of them were on Daystar now, and like I said, some of them are on every day.

00:19:56.339 --> 00:20:01.383
And I'm telling you, it's time to really watch who you are listening to.

00:20:01.384 --> 00:20:07.191
This is a very, very serious time. It's time to get your lamp full of oil.

00:20:07.192 --> 00:20:12.992
Just like what the Bible talks about, there will be ten virgins.

00:20:12.993 --> 00:20:22.879
Five had their lamps full of oil and five were not waiting for the bridegroom to come and get them, and their lamps ran dry.

00:20:22.880 --> 00:20:32.396
It's time for you to get on fire for Jesus and have an uncompromising walk with him like you've never walked with him before.

00:20:32.397 --> 00:20:38.478
It's time to throw away the world's stuff and throw away all that garbage.

00:20:38.479 --> 00:20:45.150
Yes, we fall, but we get back up. Yes, it's by grace we're saved through faith.

00:20:45.151 --> 00:20:57.965
But I'm telling you that if you're walking in compromise and you know you're in sin and you're walking in it and you're doing it on purpose, you better get it out of your life as fast as possible.

00:20:57.966 --> 00:21:12.168
You need to go and repent and fall on the mercy seat of the Lord and say, "Father, help me to deal with this,"and he'll wash you clean by the blood of the lamb and by the word of your testimony.

00:21:12.169 --> 00:21:21.337
You are free. But I'm telling you, it's not a time to play games and walk in compromise and live in the world.

00:21:21.338 --> 00:21:28.166
Yes, we mess up; things happen. But we don't consciously do it on purpose.

00:21:28.167 --> 00:21:33.497
If you say a bad word or whatever, you don't go out and say, 'I'm just going to go out and have fun.

00:21:33.498 --> 00:21:40.716
I'm going to sow my wild oats and have fun because I have Jesus in my heart and I'm going to live the way I want to and I'm going to make it.'No, you're not.

00:21:40.717 --> 00:21:43.890
You're going to get left. I'm just trying to tell you, I saw it.

00:21:43.891 --> 00:21:52.114
People say, 'There's no scripture to back that up; it's once saved, always saved.'I don't believe that. After what I saw, it's not once saved, always saved.

00:21:52.115 --> 00:22:03.972
There's a remnant of people, but there are a lot of people that get left, and they are furious because they thought they could live the way they wanted to and still have the cup of blessing to go in the rapture of the church.

00:22:03.973 --> 00:22:16.478
It didn't happen that way. I saw those Christians try to create leaders.

00:22:16.479 --> 00:22:32.668
They were trying to make colonies, like little groups of people, and they fled to the mountains and the hills where they could get away.

00:22:32.669 --> 00:22:40.128
They grabbed what they could and went up into the hills to hide.

00:22:40.129 --> 00:22:50.989
There were literally thousands of them trying to get away because they knew what was about to happen.

00:22:50.990 --> 00:23:00.534
They knew about the Bible and had a sense of what was going on, but they just lived in compromise.

00:23:00.535 --> 00:23:20.554
I'm going to tell you how they lived. They dug holes in the side of hills—massive holes that looked like little foxholes.

00:23:20.555 --> 00:23:28.809
They were like big bear caves, and they were trying to keep warm in the winter.

00:23:28.810 --> 00:23:39.234
The children born during the tribulation suffered greatly from starvation, cold, sickness, and disease.

00:23:39.235 --> 00:23:45.963
There were no vitamins to keep your D3 up; it was literal hell on earth.

00:23:45.964 --> 00:23:55.119
They had no way of really keeping their children safe and warm.

00:23:55.120 --> 00:24:14.351
I saw the government from all over the world start to use drones everywhere to look for anybody that did not have the mark of the beast.

00:24:14.352 --> 00:24:28.788
The chip in your forehead or your hand communicated to the drones. You could hear the drones; they were like swarms of bees.

00:24:28.789 --> 00:24:36.319
The Bible even talks about it looking like locusts coming out of a pit.

00:24:36.320 --> 00:24:54.157
I believe what John saw on the Isle of Patmos was probably these drones; that is just my opinion. The sky was buzzing with thousands of drones.

00:24:54.158 --> 00:25:14.639
They're all at a certain level—not a high altitude—just buzzing around at certain parts of the day looking for people who do not have the mark of the beast.

00:25:14.640 --> 00:25:37.794
They scan and come in packs, and you can hear them coming. They could sense fire if the Christians had a big fire while hiding in those hills.

00:25:37.795 --> 00:25:52.479
Those hills were being patrolled, but the Christians were smart and could get down in those holes and keep their heat hidden so infrared was not able to see it.

00:25:52.480 --> 00:26:11.190
They couldn't see the smoke if they had small fires. However, if they heard a gunshot or anything to kill wildlife, those drones could hear it from far away and would come to where that noise was.

00:26:11.191 --> 00:26:25.562
You could not shoot firearms to drop game like deer, elk, or cattle; so, they were starving.

00:26:25.563 --> 00:26:38.702
They would try to get fish or whatever they could find, but they would have to create a very small fire to be able to cook that food because you run out of supplies.

00:26:38.703 --> 00:26:48.505
Try seven years. This isn't just a couple of weeks living off the grid; this is seven years of hell.

00:26:48.506 --> 00:26:58.685
Some say it was only three and a half years, but even the first three and a half years were bad going into the great tribulation of the last three and a half years.

00:26:58.686 --> 00:27:21.519
It's all bad. I was shown they were in the foxholes. Then Jesus and I went to another place; I watched the Christians running, trying to go from place to place.

00:27:21.520 --> 00:27:37.009
They traveled at night in the dark. There were farms where the farmers were still trying to grow crops like corn.

00:27:37.010 --> 00:27:44.285
The Christians would go out and try to steal those crops in the fields during the nighttime.

00:27:44.286 --> 00:27:57.135
But the farmer would have a dog or security system and would know they were being robbed.

00:27:57.136 --> 00:28:09.599
If the farmer was trying to be nice and didn't report what he saw to the authorities, he would be punished.

00:28:09.600 --> 00:28:25.682
A lot of people say they'll take all the guns away in America, but I saw the farmers still had guns.

00:28:25.683 --> 00:28:46.455
I heard the dogs barking and the Christians running as fast as they could to grab corn, vegetables, or chickens to try to get food.

00:28:46.456 --> 00:28:59.751
Whenever someone would see these people running and call it in, I saw them putting blocks in the roads—massive barricades.

00:28:59.752 --> 00:29:11.823
The Christians would use things to spike the tires of these people. They were in black Hummers with blue lights.

00:29:11.824 --> 00:29:29.769
I saw these massive army tank-like cars with men in solid black outfits and black shields over their faces.

00:29:29.770 --> 00:29:44.004
They would drive up in these Hummer-like cars with blue lights in them; they were almost like black lights.

00:29:44.005 --> 00:29:51.143
I remember them jumping out and the Christians running as fast as they could to get away.

00:29:51.144 --> 00:30:03.204
The men jumped out with guns that I've never seen before. I've told people about this and they said they actually exist—there are prototypes.

00:30:03.205 --> 00:30:18.475
They pulled the trigger and it was like a pulse, some kind of riot control that knocked you out for a couple of minutes.

00:30:18.476 --> 00:30:31.582
They just pointed it in a direction, and as soon as that beam hit that individual, it knocked them unconscious.

00:30:31.583 --> 00:30:41.777
There was no running away. It was on the Hummers and on the men, and they would just scan the people as they were running.

00:30:41.778 --> 00:30:53.388
The people would just fall out as if they were passing out, but it didn't kill them.

00:30:53.389 --> 00:31:16.917
Then the men would walk up on them and tell them, 'Take the mark or we're going to cut your head off.'So I saw a woman and her two children that were born during the tribulation and her husband all standing there like this.

00:31:16.918 --> 00:31:31.973
They told the mother, 'If you don't take the mark and the children don't take the mark, we're going to cut those children's heads off.'And as any mother that's good would say, she was freaking out.

00:31:31.974 --> 00:31:46.071
'Don't cut my babies'heads off! I'll take the mark.'And I saw her, right before my face, take the mark of the beast. And the children took the mark of the beast.

00:31:46.072 --> 00:32:04.734
And the father said, 'No, I'll never take the mark of the beast.'And I saw those men; they pulled his head out and they had a massive sword, and they chopped his head off right before me.

00:32:04.735 --> 00:32:16.099
And I saw his head roll right before my feet. They couldn't see me, and they could not see Jesus, but Jesus told me to look.

00:32:16.100 --> 00:32:23.222
And this is something interesting: the whole time Jesus never had to speak out loud verbally to me.

00:32:23.223 --> 00:32:32.444
I could hear what he was saying by his thoughts, and he could hear what I was saying by my thoughts.

00:32:32.445 --> 00:32:39.163
I just knew it was like I was out of my body. I don't know; it was way out there, what happened.

00:32:39.164 --> 00:32:47.372
But I could smell the blood from the man that got his head cut off right before me.

00:32:47.373 --> 00:32:59.595
And the kids and the mother had no expression. The chip makes you motionless, having no emotions at all.

00:32:59.596 --> 00:33:07.631
You become like a zombie. It makes your mind instantaneously like a zombie.

00:33:07.632 --> 00:33:20.479
It's like, 'Hello, there's nothing there.'The children did not cry or wail or anything at all upset because their father just got his head cut off.

00:33:20.480 --> 00:33:32.196
And the wife didn't even act like she cared either. It was like she was not there. So, he's dead. The wife and the children are okay.

00:33:32.197 --> 00:33:37.114
They have the chip now, but they're damned to hell forever because of what happened.

00:33:37.115 --> 00:33:41.277
Now, are the children damned to hell forever? I don't believe that.

00:33:41.278 --> 00:33:47.512
There's no way. In my heart, I'm just going to say the children didn't choose it.

00:33:47.513 --> 00:33:54.775
They were forced; it was forced on them. And God's a merciful God when it comes to kids.

00:33:54.776 --> 00:34:00.405
So, I'm not going to sit here and get in a theological debate about it.

00:34:00.406 --> 00:34:05.553
I'm just telling you the kids didn't choose to take it. It was forced on them.

00:34:05.554 --> 00:34:09.045
And so, I just know God's a merciful God. Now, I don't know the condition of their soul.

00:34:09.046 --> 00:34:18.885
I know what the Bible says, that anybody who takes the mark goes to hell and they burn forever and ever.

00:34:18.886 --> 00:34:24.884
But if it was forced on you, you didn't accept it. You have to actually accept this.

00:34:24.885 --> 00:34:38.719
So, I'm just going to leave that there. You do with it what you want to, but don't criticize me in the comments. So, now I'm going to go to this.

00:34:38.720 --> 00:34:56.878
I saw in every single town, on the major highways or the roads coming into the town, they had barricades like checkpoints that everybody had to go through to come in or out of that town.

00:34:56.879 --> 00:35:04.860
And the only way you were allowed in those major cities or towns was by the mark of the beast.

00:35:04.861 --> 00:35:17.087
They scanned your hand or your forehead to get inside there to get supplies like groceries, medical, or to go to the doctor, whatever you had to do.

00:35:17.088 --> 00:35:23.653
You had to go through those major army checkpoints with these men in these black outfits.

00:35:23.654 --> 00:35:27.758
They scanned you. And I saw people on foot trying to go in there.

00:35:27.759 --> 00:35:49.394
And this is another thing: I saw that some of the people got a sore on their hand or their forehead that looked like a massive infection.

00:35:49.395 --> 00:35:55.313
It looked like a boil on their forehead or their hand that had a bruise.

00:35:55.314 --> 00:36:02.251
It looked like an infection. It had pus on it. It looked very, very painful.

00:36:02.253 --> 00:36:18.479
And I saw a woman that was standing in line who had put makeup on her hand and was trying to imitate the mark of the beast sore.

00:36:18.480 --> 00:36:29.282
She was that desperate to get into that town for food or medical supplies or whatever she needed. She was just trying to fake it.

00:36:29.283 --> 00:36:36.673
And so, when they saw that she was faking it, when they got up there to scan her hand, there was no mercy.

00:36:36.675 --> 00:36:41.570
They cut her head off right there. They killed her right there.

00:36:41.572 --> 00:36:46.799
They just cut her head off and it just rolled down the street and nobody cared.

00:36:46.800 --> 00:36:54.775
All the other people in line, like I said, are zombies. They were all standing in line; I saw it all.

00:36:54.776 --> 00:37:05.843
And they would go through these checkpoints to get groceries or whatever from coming in and out of the city.

00:37:05.844 --> 00:37:11.489
And like I said, the drones are always flying. The drones are always scanning people.

